{"TopicId":224038,"ForumId":144,"TopicTitle":"Trajectory doesn\u0027t update until after entering Ike\u0027s SOI when in orbit around Duna [Happens when apoapsis is below target body]","CreatedByName":"Navoan","CreatedById":133765,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-09T21:23:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Navoan","CreatedById":133765,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-09T21:23:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.1 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i7-14700KF | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A02070 SUPER | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeverity: Medium.\u003Cbr\u003E\nFrequency: Unsure.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nIssue:\u003Cbr\u003E\nIn orbit around Duna I expect that when my crafts trajectory enters Ike\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESoI\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E the affect on my crafts trajectory will be shown correctly, i.e. that Ike\u0027s gravity will change my trajectory.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhat is happening is that after a standard launch from Kerbin into Duna orbit, intersecting Ike\u0027s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESoI\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E doesn\u0027t show to have any impact on my orbit trajectory.\u00A0 But when passing into the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESoI\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E the trajectory is then updated.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWith a manuever node it seems like when the Periapsis is higher than ~393k (hard to get exact number) above Ike the game simply stops showing that the craft will enter the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESoI\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Uw40dh1.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002249.25\u0022 height=\u0022469\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Uw40dh1.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022AiHJKsT.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002252.00\u0022 height=\u0022547\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/AiHJKsT.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022AiHJKsT-Imgur.png.cf248d8552c52a79e4b519356f120d8a.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/monthly_2024_03/AiHJKsT-Imgur.png.cf248d8552c52a79e4b519356f120d8a.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=KerbalSpaceProgram22024-03-0921-46-08.mp4\u0026amp;fileKey=%5B!AES128GCM%5BXjcsvVxpltXBfSZCsEsyqiKdU5IYIoxf7a2ldCQfUuBW1Imn67HNtGTpo1i7NvGgOH2aq3fQYb1foY/gu9v4ZFjYuYtZOsbiLqdlYTK3svsVxstXfbTrDJyyhEwS%2BA==%5D%5B08f70e9785d622ce79ac5f1a%5D%5B15dae18037d2db58193aa6a65ae419a1%5D%5D\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EKerbalSpaceProgram22024-03-0921-46-08.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u